Dinnerbone: Making good progress on the loot tables I mentioned yesterday. Here's the end city treasure, which has enchantments: https://gist.github.com/Dinnerbone/e1417b4372d8e05c8541
Dinnerbone: One system left is predicates, which lets us (& modders & mapmakers) "gate" loot. For example, "no potions until you've been to the nether"

